Product description

Multifunctional and Durable Digital Kitchen Scale

A handy tool for homemakers, cooking, and baking professionals and enthusiasts!

Press a button to easily switch 6 weighing units, including g / kg / oz / lb/ ml /milk ml.

It is made with stainless steel design which makes cleaning so easy!

PACKAGE CONTENT:

1 x Ultrean Digital Scale

1 x User Manual

1 x CR2032

FEATURES:

  • 6-Unit Conversion
  • 4 High-precision sensors
  • LCD display
  • One-Touch Tare
  • Weighing range: 1g-5000g
  • Division value: 1g
  • Auto-Off & Backlit: 3 Minutes
  • Overload & Low Battery Reminder

Multiple Unit Conversion

Unit can be converted manually in grams, oz, pounds and milliliters. Milk volume and water volume can also be measured.

LCD Display

The unit has a negative white digital display so it is easier to read and see even in not well lit rooms.

One-Touch Tare

Tare function helps you to weigh smaller ingredients or liquids inside a container without measuring the container itself .

Accurate Measurement

With four high precision sensors, you can achieve detailed and excellent digital weight measurement.

Low Battery Prompt

Reminds you to replace the battery in time to get accurate measurement results.

Multifunctional Kitchen Scale

Help you eat properly by weighing your materials and maintain a regular diet.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    Reviewed in Canada on 18 January 2025
    Verified Purchase
    This kitchen scale is accurate and perfect for baking and cooking. The tare function is very handy, allowing you to reset the weight to zero when using bowls or containers. Its lightweight, compact, and easy to store, making it great for everyday use.

    The display is clear and simple to read, and the inclusion of batteries is a nice bonus. However, the surface can smudge easily, so regular cleaning is needed to keep it looking good.

    Overall, its a reliable and affordable scale for anyone who needs precise measurements in the kitchen. Definitely worth considering!
